tafsir[7]{c,v,t}:
  15,54,"Annabi Ibraahiima maakani ɓe - nde o ŋalɗi e ko ɓe wewliniri mo kon ɓiɗɗo - : E on wewliniray lam ɓiɗɗo e hoore ko mi nawyi kon mi ronkiti? E ko honɗum wewlinirton mi?"
  15,55,"Malaa'ikaaɓe imminaaɓe ɓen wi'ani Ibraahiima: Men wewlinirii ma goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un. Wata a jeye e taƴiiɓe e ko men wewlinir maa kon."
  15,61,"Nde Malaa'ikaaɓe imminaaɓe ɓen ardunoo ka ɓeynguure Luuti e mbaadi worɓe."
  15,62,"Annabi Luutu maakani ɓe: Ko on yimɓe ɓe anddaaka."
  15,64,"Men addanii ma goonga ka jillaa gajaate. Pellet ko men goonguɓe e ko men humpitu maa kon."
  15,69,"Huliree Alla accugol nguu faahishaaku. Wata on hoyniray ɗee kuuɗe mon kaanuɗe."
  15,70,"Yimɓe makko ɓen wi'ani mo: E men haɗaali ma weernugol gooto e yimɓe ɓen?"